Package: comrad
Type: Package
Title: R implementation of a Competitive Radiation model
Version: 1.21.0
Author: Theo Pannetier
Maintainer: Theo Pannetier <t.s.c.pannetier@rug.nl>
Description: This R package is based on the eco-evolutionary model introduced in 
    Pontarp et al.(2012), and simulates the evolution of a community where 
    individuals undergo speciation, inter- and intra-specific competition, 
    and dispersal in a spatially explicit setting.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
